To resolve this, you can change the way you establish the connection by enabling the allowLoadLocalInfile property:

    connection = DriverManager.getConnection(&quot;jdbc:mysql://192.168.1.5:3306/testdb?user=root&amp;password=pwd123&amp;allowLoadLocalInfile=true&quot;);

